# Notion Project Workflow

This is a local + Notion dual-track project.

## Start Every Session

1. Read `docs/HANDOFF.md`
2. Read `docs/notion-sync-policy.md`
3. Read `manifest.yaml` and `NOTION_INDEX.md`

## Rules

- Structure changes: update local docs and manifest before Notion
- Task status: Notion is authoritative; mirror to CSV
- Never store Notion URLs only in chat; write them to manifest and NOTION_INDEX
- Append `CHANGELOG.md` after maintenance sessions
